c: 9
v: 35
t: "Ngosuku lapho kuyoshiswa khona emlilweni wesihogo (konke lokho ababengakusebenzisi endleleni kaMvelinqangi) bese kushiswa ngakho iziphongo zabo nezinhlangothi zabo nemihlaneyabo, (kuyothiwa) “ilokhu imiphefumulo yenu eyakuqoqela ndawonye ngakho-ke yizwani lokho enanikuqoqela ndawonye"